          <h2 class="serif text-3xl text-zinc-900 mb-6 flex items-center gap-3"><span class="gold-text">1.</span> Abstract</h2>
          <div class="prose prose-zinc max-w-none leading-8 text-[15.5px]">
            <p><strong>EFIKCOIN (EFC)</strong> is a community-driven BEP-20 token on BNB Smart Chain, designed for human utility rather than speculation. It was created to provide simple, low-cost, and transparent financial tools that serve real people in real communities.</p>
            <p class="mt-4">With a fixed supply of 1,000,000,000 EFC, EFC introduces sustainable mechanics: an 8% APY staking rate, a claimable rewards system, near-zero transfer fees, and a fair airdrop distribution model. All core contracts are verified on BscScan, and key assets are preserved on IPFS.</p>
            <p class="mt-4">Our thesis is straightforward: when digital value is built in <em>Truth, Love, and Peace</em>, it can sustain human lives, fund local initiatives, and remain resilient across market cycles. EFC is not a promise of profit—it is infrastructure for empowerment.</p>
